TITLE: Project
DESCRIPTION: The study the data is coming from

TITLE: Acknowledgement
DESCRIPTION: Acknowledgement of an individual or group involved in a project.

TITLE: Sample
DESCRIPTION: Biospecimen information that links subjects to samples including sample's provider and source.

TITLE: Subject
DESCRIPTION: An individual participant in the study with baseline measurements.

TITLE: Demographic
DESCRIPTION: Data for the characterization of the patient by means of segementing the population (e.g. characterization by age, sex, or race).

TITLE: Lipidomics Assay
DESCRIPTION: Details about the methods that produced the lipidomics file

TITLE: Metabolomics Assay
DESCRIPTION: Details about the methods that produced the metabolomics file

TITLE: Proteomics Assay
DESCRIPTION: Details about the methods that produced the proteomics file

TITLE: Genomics Assay
DESCRIPTION: Details about the methods that produced the genomics file

TITLE: Unaligned Reads File
DESCRIPTION: Data file containing raw reads from a genomics assay

TITLE: Alignment Workflow
DESCRIPTION: Metadata for the alignment pipeline used to align reads during genomic harmonisation
